#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn10.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn10.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Indakavagga "
msgstr "1. With Indaka "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn10.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Punabbasusutta "
msgstr "7. With Punabbasu "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.210, sc1
msgctxt "sn10.7:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.7:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā bhikkhū nibbānapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti. "
msgstr "Now at that time the Buddha was educating, encouraging, firing up, and inspiring the mendicants with a Dhamma talk about extinguishment. "

msgctxt "sn10.7:1.3"
msgid "Te ca bhikkhū aṭṭhiṃ katvā manasi katvā sabbacetasā samannāharitvā ohitasotā dhammaṃ suṇanti. "
msgstr "And those mendicants were paying heed, paying attention, engaging wholeheartedly, and lending an ear. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.7:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho punabbasumātā yakkhinī puttake evaṃ tosesi: "
msgstr "Then the native spirit Punabbasu’s Mother soothed her little children, saying: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.453, sc2, verse-num-sc828
msgctxt "sn10.7:2.1"
msgid "“Tuṇhī uttarike hohi, "
msgstr "“Hush, little Uttarā! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:2.2"
msgid "tuṇhī hohi punabbasu; "
msgstr "Hush, Punabbasu! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:2.3"
msgid "Yāvāhaṃ buddhaseṭṭhassa, "
msgstr "For I want to listen to the teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:2.4"
msgid "dhammaṃ sossāmi satthuno. "
msgstr "of the Teacher, the supreme Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3, verse-num-sc829
msgctxt "sn10.7:3.1"
msgid "Nibbānaṃ bhagavā āha, "
msgstr "Since the Blessed One spoke of extinguishment, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:3.2"
msgid "sabbaganthappamocanaṃ; "
msgstr "the release from all ties, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:3.3"
msgid "Ativelā ca me hoti, "
msgstr "I have a lasting love "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:3.4"
msgid "asmiṃ dhamme piyāyanā. "
msgstr "for this teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4, verse-num-sc830
msgctxt "sn10.7:4.1"
msgid "Piyo loke sako putto, "
msgstr "In this world, your own child is dear; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:4.2"
msgid "piyo loke sako pati; "
msgstr "in this world, your own husband is dear; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:4.3"
msgid "Tato piyatarā mayhaṃ, "
msgstr "but even greater than that is my love "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:4.4"
msgid "assa dhammassa magganā. "
msgstr "for this teaching’s quest. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5, verse-num-sc831
msgctxt "sn10.7:5.1"
msgid "Na hi putto pati vāpi, "
msgstr "For neither son nor husband, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:5.2"
msgid "piyo dukkhā pamocaye; "
msgstr "dear as they are, can free you from suffering; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:5.3"
msgid "Yathā saddhammassavanaṃ, "
msgstr "as listening to the true teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:5.4"
msgid "dukkhā moceti pāṇinaṃ. "
msgstr "frees living creatures from suffering. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6, verse-num-sc832
msgctxt "sn10.7:6.1"
msgid "Loke dukkhaparetasmiṃ, "
msgstr "In this world mired in suffering, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:6.2"
msgid "Jarāmaraṇasaṃyute; "
msgstr "fettered by old age and death, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:6.3"
msgid "Jarāmaraṇamokkhāya, "
msgstr "I want to listen to the teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:6.4"
msgid "Yaṃ dhammaṃ abhisambudhaṃ; "
msgstr "that the Buddha awakened to, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:6.5"
msgid "Taṃ dhammaṃ sotumicchāmi, "
msgstr "which frees you from old age and death. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:6.6"
msgid "Tuṇhī hohi punabbasū”ti. "
msgstr "So hush, Punabbasu!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.454, sc7, verse-num-sc833
msgctxt "sn10.7:7.1"
msgid "“Ammā na byāharissāmi, "
msgstr "“Mom, I’m not speaking, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:7.2"
msgid "tuṇhībhūtāyamuttarā; "
msgstr "and Uttarā is silent, too. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:7.3"
msgid "Dhammameva nisāmehi, "
msgstr "Focus just on the teaching, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:7.4"
msgid "saddhammassavanaṃ sukhaṃ; "
msgstr "for it’s nice to listen to the true teaching. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:7.5"
msgid "Saddhammassa anaññāya, "
msgstr "And it’s because we haven’t understood the teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:7.6"
msgid "ammā dukkhaṃ carāmase. "
msgstr "that we’ve lived in suffering, Mom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8, verse-num-sc834
msgctxt "sn10.7:8.1"
msgid "Esa devamanussānaṃ, "
msgstr "For those who are lost, gods and humans, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:8.2"
msgid "sammūḷhānaṃ pabhaṅkaro; "
msgstr "he shines a light. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:8.3"
msgid "Buddho antimasārīro, "
msgstr "The Buddha, bearing his final body, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:8.4"
msgid "dhammaṃ deseti cakkhumā”ti. "
msgstr "the Seer teaches Dhamma.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9, verse-num-sc835
msgctxt "sn10.7:9.1"
msgid "“Sādhu kho paṇḍito nāma, "
msgstr "“It’s good that my child’s so astute, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:9.2"
msgid "putto jāto uresayo; "
msgstr "this child I bore and suckled! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:9.3"
msgid "Putto me buddhaseṭṭhassa, "
msgstr "My child loves the pure teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:9.4"
msgid "dhammaṃ suddhaṃ piyāyati. "
msgstr "of the supreme Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.455, sc10, verse-num-sc836
msgctxt "sn10.7:10.1"
msgid "Punabbasu sukhī hohi, "
msgstr "Punabbasu, may you be happy! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:10.2"
msgid "ajjāhamhi samuggatā; "
msgstr "Today, I rise. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:10.3"
msgid "Diṭṭhāni ariyasaccāni, "
msgstr "Hear me too, Uttarā: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.7:10.4"
msgid "uttarāpi suṇātu me”ti. "
msgstr "I have seen the noble truths!”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
